WEBVTT

00:01.880 --> 00:03.360
Previously on Medium:

00:03.370 --> 00:06.350
Name's Autumn Colville. Mother
reported her missing yesterday.

00:09.150 --> 00:12.400
The blood. And that corpse.

00:12.670 --> 00:14.550
What corpse?

00:16.160 --> 00:18.940
Scanlon just called. They found
the remains of Autumn Colville.

00:18.950 --> 00:20.500
There were several more
duffel bags down there.

00:20.520 --> 00:24.120
When they opened them up,they found the
butchered body parts of two more girls.

00:24.140 --> 00:26.370
Looks like we got
ourselves a serial killer.

00:26.400 --> 00:29.020
I got a call from Ashley's father today.

00:29.330 --> 00:32.800
He's convinced that his daughter is
sharing her antianxiety medication with you.

00:32.820 --> 00:36.750
There's this girl,and she won't leave me alone
and she won't let me study or concentrate...

00:36.780 --> 00:38.510
Wait a second. Hold on. What girl?

00:38.520 --> 00:40.690
Stacey Anne Burrows.

00:40.710 --> 00:44.310
Stacey Anne--
is she dead?

00:45.630 --> 00:51.340
We decided that if the doctor thinks that this
medicine will improve the quality of your life,

00:51.350 --> 00:54.640
I will try to get that
appointment as soon as possible.

00:54.650 --> 00:56.820
Allison Dubois? I'm Caitlyn Lynch.

00:56.830 --> 00:58.670
I'm with the Lydecker Corporation.

00:58.700 --> 01:00.190
You're offering me a job?

01:00.240 --> 01:03.010
What exactly does it mean when
they say "high six figures"?

01:03.040 --> 01:04.680
Means you need to call her tomorrow.

01:04.709 --> 01:06.380
You need to find out
what this is all about.

01:06.410 --> 01:07.850
So you think I should take it?

01:07.890 --> 01:09.380
How do you not take it?

01:09.420 --> 01:12.680
These are employee dossiers.

01:12.690 --> 01:14.870
I'd like you to spend
some time with them.

01:14.880 --> 01:18.600
See if there's anyone among
this group that gives you pause.

01:18.620 --> 01:21.030
Well,he's really the only
person who jumped out at me.

01:21.070 --> 01:23.480
And this is the only employee
that you're worried about?

01:23.510 --> 01:27.200
He's Justin Lydecker.
Mr. Lydecker's son.

01:27.210 --> 01:31.670
Your father is interested in
my impressions of things,people,

01:31.710 --> 01:34.380
which is why I think he
wanted me to sit down with you.

01:34.390 --> 01:35.990
Yeah. That's what I figured.

01:36.000 --> 01:40.480
He wants you to tell him if his only son
is permanently screwed up or if I can be...

01:40.490 --> 01:41.850
salvaged.

01:41.870 --> 01:43.840
Lee,it's me. I just had another dream.

01:43.850 --> 01:46.280
I think it happened
again,another murder.

01:46.310 --> 01:50.130
The dreams you've been having about the murders,did
you mention your dreams to your colleague?

01:50.160 --> 01:52.650
Dreams that we're talking about
have nothing to do with Lydecker.

01:52.690 --> 01:56.900
Your dreams,your impressions,they
belong to Lydecker now.

01:56.940 --> 02:00.040
They are actually the intellectual
property of our company.

02:00.080 --> 02:02.910
If you ever breach your contract again,

02:02.950 --> 02:08.789
I will litigate you with a vigor unlike
anything you have ever experienced in your life.

02:15.670 --> 02:16.590
Justin.

